      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels just like it did the day it rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve been super careful with it, keeping it garage-stored and pampered, so it\u2019s basically spotless. It drives like a total dream and is ready for someone new to love it as much as I have. You\u2019ve gotta see it for yourself!",
