    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 inline-six. This specimen is mechanically flawless, boasting a crisp 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by factory individual throttle bodies. Precise handling is ensured by a recently refreshed suspension geometry and a rear subframe that has been professionally reinforced\u2014a critical preventative measure for this chassis. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, while the variable M differential lock ensures optimal power delivery. Complete service records confirm that both the Vanos system and rod bearings have been addressed, ensuring this high-revving powerplant operates at peak volumetric efficiency. Original factory finish with consistent paint depth across all panels.",
