      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. Meticulously maintained by a single enthusiast owner, this car has been strictly garage-kept and protected with a professional-grade multi-layer ceramic coating, ensuring the paint retains a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark, scratch, or stone chip. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the factory floor mats have been protected by deep-dish liners since day one. Every electronic feature, from the high-resolution infotainment system to the climate-controlled seating, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach. It comes with a comprehensive binder of service records, documenting every scheduled maintenance and fluid flush performed exclusively at the authorized dealership. The engine bay is immaculate, and the undercarriage is free of any corrosion or road debris. This car represents the pinnacle of its model year, suited for a discerning buyer who accepts nothing less than perfection. Included are both original keys, the owner's manual, and a custom-fit car cover.",
